commit.message:
configure.ac: Guard include of <ieeefp.h>.

	* configure.ac: Guard include of <ieeefp.h>.
	* configure: Rebuilt.

From-SVN: r218032

files.patch:

+2014-11-24  John David Anglin  <danglin@gcc.gnu.org>
+
+	* configure.ac: Guard include of <ieeefp.h>.

+
 2014-11-21  H.J. Lu  <hongjiu.lu@intel.com>

 fi
